These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Hobby: board-games, drawing, magic-tricks, video-games
Job: social-worker, freelancer, photographer, firefighter
1. Job:freelancer is on the left of Job:social-worker##1
2. Hobby:board-games == Job:firefighter##1
3. Job:photographer is on the right of Job:social-worker##1
4. Hobby:drawing is on the left of Job:firefighter##1
5. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Job:social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | video-games | magic-tricks | drawing | board-games   |
| Job   | freelancer  | social-worker     | photographer   | firefighter |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Color: mauve, coral, azure, light-blue
Flower: bellflower, daisy, dahlia, lily
1. Color:light-blue == Flower:daisy##1
2. Color:mauve is on the far right##1
3. Color:coral is on the right of Color:light-blue##1
4. Color:light-blue is on the right of Flower:dahlia##1
5. Flower:daisy is on the left of Flower:bellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | azure | light-blue | coral | mauve    |
| Flower   | dahlia    | daisy      | bellflower | lily |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
