3. Sport:volleyball is on the far right##1
4. Sport:golf is on the right of Food:plum##1
5. Food:cabbage is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Food         | lettuce | plum | cabbage   | cucumber |
| Sport   | tennis   | badminton | golf | volleyball         |

