2. Flower:orchid is on the left of Movie-Genre:animation##1
3. Movie-Genre:documentary is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
4. Movie-Genre:animation == Flower:tulip##1
5. Flower:rose is on the left of Movie-Genre:thriller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
